          "COMMENT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The charge distribution of residual nuclei at",
                " spallation of Nb-93 by bremsstrahlung photons with",
                " maximum gamma energy of 4.5 GeV was investigated.",
                "Studying the isobar charge dispersion and comparing",
                " the obtained data with results of hardronic nuclear",
                " reactions one is able to elucidate some regularities",
                " of the nuclear spallation as well as to predict the",
                " production probability of yields of the residual",
                " nuclei which are difficult to measure by activation",
                " methods. To estimate the reaction yield quantitatevely",
                " a five-parameter rudstam formula was used.",
                "The nature and properties of isobaric and mass yields",
                " are discussed and compared with calculations of the",
                " two-step cascade-evaporation model."
              ]
            }
          ],
